== 爭議 ==
===視頻魔術爭議===
2012年，他在youtube發表的魔術影片登上[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]，隨後被認為其手法可能以電視後製效果（[[視頻魔術|視頻魔術]]）為主，在台湾引發爭議。如「麵團變成法國長麵包」的魔術中，被部分網友以定格檢視其影片，被網友猜測至少一個以上的影片框中存在著影像後製時失誤的遮罩。「小籠包光速移動」的魔術表演中的路人，網友發現可能是臨時演員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20121229/146818.htm?from=fb_et_news |language= |title=Yif秀魔術　網友抓包爆乳辣妹是臨演 |publisher=東森新聞 |date= |accessdate= |archive-date=2014-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112064113/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20121229/146818.htm?from=fb_et_news |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

台湾魔術師[[粘立人|粘立人]]認為Yif使用電影特效假冒魔術<ref>{{cite web  |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20121221/157799/  |language=  |title=粘立人怒轟Yif　95%表演攏是假  |publisher=蘋果日報  |date=2012-12-21  |accessdate=  |archive-date=2012-12-31  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121231053912/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20121221/157799  |dead-url=no  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_detailpage&v=4r8b2LVJM5U#t=58s |language= |title=麵團變麵包 粘立人踢爆Yif造假 |publisher=民視新聞 |date=2012-12-21 |accessdate= |archive-date=2014-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619175437/http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_detailpage&v=4r8b2LVJM5U#t=58s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一台灣魔術師[[羅賓_(魔術師)|羅賓]]則表態「加工魔術視頻的歪風是魔術師的取巧、偷懶和墮落！」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?no=743673 |language= |title=羅賓轟Yif加工魔術墮落　粘立人臉書遭刪 |publisher=自由時報 |date=2012-12-27 |accessdate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102194352/http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?no=743673 |archivedate=2014-01-02 }}</ref>。饒舌歌手[[大支|大支]]則自行以後製軟體拍攝了一則領宣導領養的短片，重現了Yif的魔術效果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?no=745263&type=%E5%BD%B1%E5%8A%87|language=|title=大支仿YIF魔術　網友大讚|publisher=自由時報|date=2012-12-31|accessdate=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130104185701/http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?no=745263&type=%E5%BD%B1%E5%8A%87|archivedate=2013-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20121231/159209/%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%94%B1%E9%A5%92%E8%88%8C%E3%80%80%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E8%AE%8A%E9%AD%94%E8%A1%93%E9%85%B8Yif |language= |title=大支不唱饒舌　拍片變魔術酸Yif |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2012-12-31 |accessdate= |archive-date=2013-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103011616/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/entertainment/20121231/159209/%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%94%B1%E9%A5%92%E8%88%8C%E3%80%80%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E8%AE%8A%E9%AD%94%E8%A1%93%E9%85%B8Yif |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但大支說，其實他無意要酸Yif，只盼藉影片呼籲大家重視流浪動物，別棄養貓咪。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/2009Cti/Channel/Showbiz/showbiz-news-cnt/0,5020,110511+112013010200033,00.html|language=|title=大支仿Yif 空手變出貓|publisher=中國時報|date=2013-01-02|accessdate=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105041347/http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/2009Cti/Channel/Showbiz/showbiz-news-cnt/0,5020,110511+112013010200033,00.html|archivedate=2013-01-05}}</ref>。

