<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shangc.net/news/a/201602/17848_6.html |language= |title=「2016春晚Yif王亦豐魔术揭秘 |publisher=尚之潮综合 |date=2016-02-08 |accessdate= |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815140539/http://www.shangc.net/news/a/201602/17848_6.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

